<li>Denver Butson, "Drowning Ghazals (1, 2 &amp; 3)", "Four Drowning Ghazals"</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Robert_Bly" title="Robert Bly">Robert Bly</a>, <i>The Night Abraham Called to the Stars</i> and <i>My Sentence Was a Thousand Years of Joy</i></li>
